<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Lower part of a <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> front broken away at left end (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.83</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.10</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.55</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face. The area is divided into two by a patch of undressed marble, and carries two texts (a:  <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.63</measure>; b: <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.895</measure>), cut by different hands in markedly different styles.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>a: <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.024-0.025</measure>; the cutter has avoided a chip in the stone in l.1. b: third century letters, based on cursive and drawn freehand; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.01</measure>. The cutter has avoided chips in the stone.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>a. <date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>); b. <date notBefore="0201" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Third century A.D.</date></p>
</div>
